# 止蝕

(pos:動詞)  
<explanation>  
yue:停止虧損，喺股票或投資出現虧損時及時平倉，避免進一步損失（量詞：個）  
eng:to cut losses, to stop further losses by selling off a losing investment  
<eg>  
yue:唔好等住蝕太多先止蝕，要及時行動。 (m4 hou2 dang2 zyu6 seot3 daai6 seot3 hou2 zing2 seot3, yau6 zip6 sing6 haan2 dong6.)  
eng:Don't wait until you've lost too much before cutting your losses—act in time. [end of text]


